# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# DATA SECURITY — NEVER commit raw, processed, warehouse, or PII data.
# Verify with `git status` before EVERY commit. This is non-negotiable.
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Pipeline data folders (all gitignored)
data/raw/
data/processed/
data/warehouse/
data/secure/
data/reference/

